# Review Checklist

Before marking a task complete, verify:

| Area | Question |
|------|----------|
| **Requirements** | Does the diff satisfy the stated task only? |
| **Architecture** | Any ADR-level change? If yes — was it approved? |
| **Tests** | Were relevant tests run? Results honest? |
| **Docs** | Updated docs/handbook/EDL affected by the change? |
| **Risks** | Open questions, assumptions, regressions reported? |

See `docs/handbook/REVIEW_PROCESS.md`.
